4.35/5  rDev -1.4%look: 4.5 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4This will be my first ever taste of Russian River's Temptation. This beer has led me to driving all over Los Angeles to obtain it. It's even killed a car battery. So without further ado, I give you Temptation ....
