Allowing this delectable nominess to swirl in your mouth leaves it feeling tingly with a moderately dry finish.
For a sour this beer is pretty drinkable. It didn't leave my tastebuds feeling bent over and violated like some have in the past (not a bad thing mind you).
Overall I have to give Temptation two noms up. :) 1,099 charactersirishgurl4, Sep 09, 2010
