4.52/5  rDev +2.5%look: 4 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 4.5On-Tap at Monk's Cafe in a tulip glass. I've had this beer on draft several times now, I believe this is Batch 4.
