M: The body feels a bit fuller than the newest batch, but that could be the high level of carbonation. The finish is nice and dry.
D: This batch seems to be quite superior to the newest batch and I see why people rave about Temptation so much. Great flavors and a really crisp, dry, and refreshing beer. 1,019 characterswomencantsail, Feb 01, 2010
